a9221c2b2953e9bd80474ef245091f6c01a876a7.query:
INSERT INTO episode_download (title, episode, decimal, version, created_at)
VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5)
ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING
RETURNING id

cc3d550f2941462cab3aed632789689ef8f24027.query:
INSERT INTO episode_download_resolution (episode_download_id, resolution, torrent, file_name, comments, magnet, created_at)
VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7)
ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING

f7ad5ce6083c2188b258d516ed00072e4a6510a8.query:
SELECT ed.id, array_agg(edr.resolution) as resolutions
FROM episode_download ed
         JOIN episode_download_resolution edr on ed.id = edr.episode_download_id
WHERE provider = COALESCE($1, 'SubsPlease')
  AND ed.title = $2
  AND COALESCE(ed.episode, -1) = COALESCE($3, -1)
  AND COALESCE(ed.decimal, -1) = COALESCE($4, -1)
  AND COALESCE(ed.version, -1) = COALESCE($5, -1)
GROUP BY id
